{"tid":1438124,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢水政治] (偽)台灣廢水奶茶店集體自爆露紅底","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:46.000Z","uid":251186,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d543c5a447759069091120ffde91bb396c1161d7","tid":1438124,"uid":251186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:42:03.000Z","msg":"Credit: 我是台灣人 FB page<br />\n<br />\n今天晚上台灣之光們- 手搖飲料店集體自爆了<br />\n<br />\n1. 大苑子DaYungs<br />\n<br />\n「大苑子源自中國台灣，以新鮮果茶聞名海內外。2015年在內地成立第一家店&mdash;上海日月光店。」<br />\n<br />\n2. 迷客夏<br />\n<br />\n「中國台灣台南佳里、中國香港」<br />\n<br />\n3. CoCo都可發表聲明<br />\n<br />\n「都可堅決服從與支持（中國）國家法規政策，其中當然包括香港地區是中華人民共和國不可分割的一部分」<br />\n<br />\n4. 台灣貢茶微博聲明：<br />\n<br />\n「堅決支持一國兩制，香港是中國不可分割的一部分」<br />\n<br />\n5. 鹿角巷<br />\n<br />\n中國台灣、中國香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PdKeuG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PdKeuG.jpg&h=e2b0265b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqNSon2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqNSon2.jpg&h=44af4df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UT86sPH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUT86sPH.jpg&h=788b2bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHj9qBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHj9qBo.jpg&h=5558e640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfUYiWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfUYiWp.jpg&h=0d77e243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中廣為人知既貢榮，排到開巷既Alley係香港都有，大家咁醒應該會提提身邊朋友，唔會再俾錢紅色資本賺掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8c15a36279bf6a18b7545cbd67ac478e79f116","tid":1438124,"uid":251186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"co